  FROM kp."User"
  WHERE id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
  LIMIT 500;
SELECT * FROM "instance";
DROP TABLE "VM";

DELETE FROM kp.instance
WHERE id='';
DELETE * FROM kp.instance;

SELECT address, port, client_type, connection_stage, driver_name,
  driver_version, hostname, protocol_version, shard_id, ssl_cipher_suite,
  ssl_enabled, ssl_protocol, username
  FROM system.clients
  LIMIT 500;
DROP KEYSPACE kp;
CREATE KEYSPACE kp WITH replication = {'class': 'NetworkTopologyStrategy', 'replication_factor' : 3} AND durable_writes = true;
